Set inside a universe based on scientific theory, college student Sam
is inexplicably teleported to the decaying Heywood-Bowman facility

laws of physics. The Catalyst, one variant of a line of emergency and
industrial tools, allows the user to temporarily walk on water, climb
falling water, run faster, and stop objects in mid-air to create
stepping stones
